    <S id="S1">
        <FORM>4 Ni-pou-vavau-en-nau-kow ki kidi tou næi: ni-ma lymmou lymmou-koh ki poungas ka ni-phæ-en-nau paka-poungas jau-an.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S2">
        <FORM>5 Ra hnyn pou-vavau-a ki kidi jau-an ymhou Rama ki kidi ka akoume'-en-nau ym hou-an, rou ä'ou-ssi appa ta næi.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S3">
        <FORM>6 Ni-pou-pænæh-koh ki Na-nang-hou tou kæ'uloung-an ka ni-phæ-en-hou jau-an tou næi. A-mhou ta neni, ka ni-phæ-en-hou ta neni jau-an, ka ni-hma ta neni ki sou-oho.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S4">
        <FORM>7 Hnyn kmalang-ato ta neni ka mamang, ka ni-phæ-en-hou jau-an, ka na â-mhou ta anna.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S5">
        <FORM>8 Ka sou k'anna ka ni-phæ-en-hou jau-an, na pæ p'ǣ-au nei-ni-æn, ka ni-atta-ryh-en nein ta anna, ka d'lligh-âto kmalang ka ni-tæ'i-koua-en-nau makka-rbo ymhou-an, ka tna-'msing-ato ta neni ka ni-padingi-en-hou jau-an.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S6">
        <FORM>9 Tmoumymmya-koh alei neini-æn: Assi-koh tmoumym-mia alei ki næi, râ alei-appa neini-æn ka ni-phæ-en-hou jau-an, alei ka â-'mhou ta neni.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S7">
        <FORM>10 Ka ymmud ki â-jau, â-'mhou-appa, ka â-mhou a-jau-ap-</FORM>
    </S>
